{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"39b409fa84","title":"湖北麻城县扩大干部会议简报第六期","origin":"湖北省某档案馆","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"780e4fff0b","index":0,"year":1960,"month":12,"day":11,"articleId":"39b409fa84"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-dayuejin","name":"中国大跃进-大饥荒数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-dayuejin":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a7dbe1d213","type":"title","text":"湖北麻城县扩大干部会议简报第六期","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"27216c01d8","type":"subtitle","text":"说话要留心","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"da1ac80acc","type":"paragraph","text":"龟山茶厂组织干事周纸新说：“万人大会解决了一些问题，但好多问题并没有解决。我这次来是看领导上是么样的心，我就抱什么样的态度。有的说得，有的说不得。能说的就说，不能说的就不说。因此，说话要留心”。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"6219064599","type":"subtitle","text":"态度是两个字，任务只有一条","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"2e9f829818","type":"paragraph","text":"龟山熊家铺管理区秘书熊楚伯说：“我来学习抱的态度就是‘两个字’：一是‘听’，一是‘看’。要说，是没有什么说的。我的任务只有一条，就是搞表格”。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"cb8a650876","type":"subtitle","text":"怕么事","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"ecbcccbd30","type":"paragraph","text":"中一碰畈总支书记孔祥安同志说：“反右派我不怕，划右派都是一些历史有污点的人，我是讨米出身，有话就是要说，怕么事”。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"949727ffd9","type":"subtitle","text":"要整就整","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"96c65cc6f6","type":"paragraph","text":"龟山“三八”茶厂曾祥思说：“整风我没有什么可整，上级叫我们么样做就么样做，做错了我没有什么责任，要整就整”。","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"f1e044c5d1","type":"subtitle","text":"两个账报不出，肯定要挨整","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"04e9464c75","type":"paragraph","text":"走马岗总支书记江志茂同志说：“这次来开会，是两个账报不出：一个是产量账报不出，二个是任务未完成，肯定挨整”。","index":10,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"7b2dcb6e31","type":"subtitle","text":"过去的工作是大家哄","index":11,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"},{"id":"5aad80274e","type":"paragraph","text":"铁门公社毛家大垸徐正福说：“过去的工作是你哄我，我哄你，明知做的不对，就是不敢说”。","index":12,"publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84"}],"page":{"id":"cc4b575fc6","publicationId":"CCRD-dayuejin","articleId":"39b409fa84","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}